                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/20/237301566/dfe34a988201bda693cadf10fb3a2281_1632472243625685500.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "October 15, 2020",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "This tale began a thousand years ago, when Mondstadt's rulers fell from grace. The southern lion their crowns to the earth did throw, and the west wind arose and took their place.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The guardian of the north returned, and near to the wolven wood he drew. The Four Winds blew each in their turn, and united they built Mondstadt anew.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
